{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless Unique Matches</h2>With 3 game modes, different arenas, multiple gadgets, rocket boosters, gravity modifiers, and heaps of ragdoll physics, every match will be different in BOTSU.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Basketball_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sandbox Sports</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> BOXBALL - Get the ball in the goal!<br></li><li>SUMO SURVIVAL - Don\u2019t fall in the lava, be the last one standing!<br></li><li>STOCKPILE - Collect boxes and steal from the other team!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Stockpile_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Split-Screen &amp; Online Multiplayer</h2>Party up in 4-player split-screen and go head-to-head with online teams in matches with up to 8 players 4v4. Hang out with your friends in the sandbox social space between matches.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Split_Screen_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Acrobatic Athletes</h2>These aren\u2019t some sluggish ragdolls. You\u2019re a robot athlete at the height of your career. You can sprint,  jump, flip, climb, breakdance, fly and break through the sound barrier with your over-powered rocket boosters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Physics_Kick_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Physics-Based Fighting</h2>Combine acrobatics with combat to triple flip kick your opponents, or wrestle them in mid-air while flying upside-down. Anything is possible if you can pull it off.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Sumo_Grab_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Your Bot</h2>Level up and show off your awesome outfits. Combine any outfit with different heads, bodies, arms, legs and feet to create something truly unique.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Outfits_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gadgets</h2>Gadgets are your silly superpowers: grappling-hooks, balloons, sticky-bombs, and impulse waves work on anything, like other players, objects or the environment. Get creative and invent new ways to use them! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Gadgets_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Theatre Replay Mode</h2>Every silly ragdoll moment and every awesome victory is captured by the replay system, so you can play it back in slo-mo and work out what on earth just happened. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Theatre_Replay_1.gif?t=1731948387\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Indie Game</h2>Botsu is made by Peculiar Pixels, a one-person indie studio.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/TikTok_Banner.png?t=1731948387\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/extras/Instagram_Banner.png?t=1731948387\" /><br>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731948387","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731948387","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731948387","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/885160/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731948387","categories":[{"description":"Single